                        <interp inst="t18501125-name-323" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES MARSHALL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, N</hi> 166). I produce a certificate of Hawkins' conviction at Clerkenwell—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted Jan., 1849, and confined two months</hi>)—I was present—he is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18501125-name-324" type="witnessName">
